---
<section class="section connect" id="connect">
  <header class="section-header">
    <div>
      <p class="section-eyebrow">§ 06 — Let's talk</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">If something <em>resonates,</em> reach out.</h2>
    </div>
    <span class="section-num-big" aria-hidden="true">06</span>
  </header>
  <p class="connect-pull reveal">If your team is scoping digital transformation, cybersecurity, cloud or <abbr title="User Experience">UX</abbr> work, or doing early vendor research for someone who is, send me a message. Decision-maker or not, doesn't matter. Twenty minutes is enough to know if a second conversation makes sense.</p>

  <div class="connect-list">
    <a class="connect-link reveal" href="https://linkedin.com/in/vishnu-sudhan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <span class="connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <span class="connect-type">LinkedIn</span>
      <span class="connect-val">linkedin.com/in/vishnu-sudhan</span>
      <span class="connect-ext" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </a>
    <a class="connect-link email-link reveal delay-1" href="#" data-user="hello" data-domain="vishnusudhan.com" aria-label="Reveal email address">
      <span class="connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <span class="connect-type">Email</span>
      <span class="connect-val email-val">click to reveal</span>
      <span class="connect-ext" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="connect-closing reveal">Based in Chennai, working with teams across <abbr title="Asia-Pacific">APAC</abbr>.</p>
</section>

<style>
  .connect { padding: 0 var(--gutter) 64px; border-bottom: none; }
  .connect-pull {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.4vw, 24px);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 4px 0 40px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .connect-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .connect-link {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 28px 100px 1fr 24px;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: relative;
    transition: padding 0.5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .connect-link:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .connect-link:hover { padding-left: 16px; }
  .connect-link::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -1px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .connect-link:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .connect-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform 0.5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .connect-link:hover .connect-arrow { transform: translateX(8px); }

  .connect-type {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .connect-val {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 24px);
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.4s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .connect-link:hover .connect-val { color: var(--accent); }
  .connect-ext {
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: right;
    transition: color 0.4s var(--ease-out), transform 0.5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .connect-link:hover .connect-ext {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translate(4px, -4px);
  }

  .connect-closing {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .connect-link {
      grid-template-columns: 24px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .connect-type { grid-column: 2; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .connect-val { grid-column: 2; font-size: 18px; word-break: break-all; }
    .connect-ext { display: none; }
    .connect-link:hover { padding-left: 8px; }
  }
</style>
